                    <span>In the movie, the twister destroys a drive-in while The Shining is showing on the screen. One could only imagine that this amounted to a review of The Shining. I don't agree with this review. The Shining is a very good movie.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">the suck zone</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
